<m1><ue5><m0>CHANGING TIMES:<m0> Carol Hobson teaches kindergarten at Chapel Trail Elementary in Pembroke Pines. Now, it's a 6-hour day. Next year, because of crowding, two four-hour sessions will be offered. Two other schools, Silver Palms and Country Isles, are in the same boat.<ql>
